ved result after fix: focused tests passed, SDK API metadata is current after merging `main`, no conflict markers/whitespace issues remain, OpenAI/xAI/OpenCode Go model-list commands return the expected OpenClaw row shape, OpenAI OAuth maps 4 live Codex/ChatGPT models, OpenCode Go returns 18 available live rows, and xAI OAuth live `/v1/models` returns `grok-composer-2.5-fast` through the PR provider catalog mapper.\n\nWhat was not tested: authenticated completion calls for every discovered model were not run; this proof is scoped to live model-list discovery and OpenClaw catalog row mapping.\n",
